This package was originally called mythbuntu-diskless and was changed by 
Lars Op den Kamp <lars@opdenkamp.eu> for XBMC.


This package was debianized by Michael Haas <laga@laga.ath.cx> on
Thu, 31 Jan 2008 00:15:37 +0100.

It can be downloaded from https://code.launchpad.net/~mythbuntu/mythbuntu/mb-diskless

Many files were originally derived from the LTSP package found in Ubuntu.

